tiles.title: Load Items Duration by Item Count
README.md
tiles.markdownText: This page tracks the reliability and usage of the 'Open in VS Code' feature.

queries.text:
_events
| summarize Sessions = dcount(VSCodeSessionId) by Day = startofday(ClientTimestamp)
| order by Day asc

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/create"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isempty(['_ItemType']) or ItemType == ['_ItemType']
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/create"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| where not(Message contains 'Workspace creation is not enabled for the user')
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/open"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isempty(['_ItemType']) or ItemType == ['_ItemType']
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| summarize Sessions = dcount(VSCodeSessionId) by Platform
| order by Sessions desc

_events
| where EventName endswith "extension/error"
| extend ErrorMessage = tostring(Properties['errormessage'])
| where ErrorMessage != "auth-error"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| summarize Errors = count() by Day = startofday(ClientTimestamp)
| order by Day asc

_events
| where EventName endswith "extension/error"
| extend ErrorMessage = tostring(Properties['errormessage'])
| where ErrorMessage != "auth-error"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| extend Fault = tostring(Properties['fault'])
| extend NonLocalizedMessage = tostring(Properties['nonlocalizedmessage'])
| summarize ErrorCount = count() by Fault = coalesce(NonLocalizedMessage, Fault, "Unknown")
| order by ErrorCount desc
| take 50

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/update"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isempty(['_ItemType']) or ItemType == ['_ItemType']
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/delete"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isempty(['_ItemType']) or ItemType == ['_ItemType']
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/export"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/load-items"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'FeatureNotAvailable')
| extend State = tobool(Properties["succeeded"])
| summarize Success = countif(State == true), Failed = countif(State == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")
| project SuccessRateString

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/create"
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isnotempty(ItemType)
| summarize Count = count() by ItemType
| order by Count desc

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/open"
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isnotempty(ItemType)
| summarize Count = count() by ItemType
| order by Count desc

_events
| where EventName in ("fabric.vscode-fabric/item/create", "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/open", "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/update", "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/create", "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/open", "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/load-items")
| extend Duration_ms = todouble(Measures['activitydurationinmilliseconds'])
| where isnotempty(Duration_ms)
| summarize P50 = round(percentile(Duration_ms, 50) / 1000, 2), P90 = round(percentile(Duration_ms, 90) / 1000, 2), P95 = round(percentile(Duration_ms, 95) / 1000, 2), Count = count() by Operation = EventName
| order by P90 desc

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/item/create"
| extend Duration_ms = todouble(Measures['activitydurationinmilliseconds'])
| where isnotempty(Duration_ms)
| summarize P90_seconds = round(percentile(Duration_ms, 90) / 1000, 2) by Day = startofday(ClientTimestamp)
| order by Day asc

_events
| where EventName == "fabric.vscode-fabric/workspace/load-items"
| extend Duration_ms = todouble(Measures['activitydurationinmilliseconds'])
| extend ItemCount = toint(Properties['itemcount'])
| where isnotempty(Duration_ms) and isnotempty(ItemCount)
| where ItemCount <= 200
| summarize P50 = round(percentile(Duration_ms, 50) / 1000, 2), P90 = round(percentile(Duration_ms, 90) / 1000, 2) by ItemCountBucket = bin(ItemCount, 10)
| order by ItemCountBucket asc

_events
| where EventName endswith "handle-uri"
| extend TargetEnvironment = tostring(Properties["targetenvironment"])
| extend UriQuery = tostring(Properties["query"])
| extend Duration_seconds = toreal(Measures["activitydurationinmilliseconds"])/1000
| project EventName, ClientTimestamp, TargetEnvironment, UriQuery, Duration_seconds, Properties, Measures
| summarize eventCount=count() by bin(ClientTimestamp, 1d)

_events
| where EventName endswith "handle-uri"
| extend TargetEnvironment = tostring(Properties["targetenvironment"])
| extend UriQuery = tostring(Properties["query"])
| extend Duration_seconds = toreal(Measures["activitydurationinmilliseconds"])/1000
| extend Error = tostring(Properties["message"])
| extend Callstack = tostring(Properties["callstack"])
| where not(Error contains 'Not signed in')
| extend Result = (Error == "")
| summarize Success = countif(Result == true), Failed = countif(Result == false) by ClientTimestamp=endofday(ClientTimestamp)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| make-series SuccessRate=max(SuccessRate) default=double(null) on ClientTimestamp step 1d
| extend SuccessRate = series_fill_forward(SuccessRate)

_events
| where EventName endswith "handle-uri"
| extend TargetEnvironment = tostring(Properties["targetenvironment"])
| extend UriQuery = tostring(Properties["uriquery"])
| extend Duration_seconds = toreal(Measures["activitydurationinmilliseconds"])/1000
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| extend Callstack = tostring(Properties["callstack"])
| where tostring(Properties['succeeded']) == 'false'
| project ClientTimestamp, TargetEnvironment, Message, Callstack,  UriQuery,VSCodeSessionId, Duration_seconds, Properties, Measures

_events
| where EventName endswith "handle-uri"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| where not(Message contains 'Not signed in')
| extend TargetEnvironment = tostring(Properties["targetenvironment"])
| extend UriQuery = tostring(Properties["query"])
| extend Duration_seconds = toreal(Measures["activitydurationinmilliseconds"])/1000
| extend Error = tostring(Properties["message"])
| extend Callstack = tostring(Properties["callstack"])
| extend Result = (Error == "")
| summarize Success = countif(Result == true), Failed = countif(Result == false)
| extend SuccessRate = round((Success * 1.0 / (Success + Failed))*100, 1)
| extend SuccessRateString = strcat(tostring(SuccessRate), "%")

_events
| where EventName endswith "handle-uri"
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| where not(Message contains 'Cancel')
| extend TargetEnvironment = tostring(Properties["targetenvironment"])
| extend UriQuery = tostring(Properties["uriquery"])
| extend Duration_seconds = toreal(Measures["activitydurationinmilliseconds"])/1000
| extend Message = tostring(Properties["message"])
| extend Callstack = tostring(Properties["callstack"])
| where tostring(Properties['succeeded']) == 'false'
| summarize count() by Message
| as Result
| extend Percent = round(100.0 * count_ / toscalar(Result | summarize sum(count_)), 0)
| order by Percent desc

RawEventsVSCodeExt
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric"
| where ServerTimestamp between (['_startTime'] .. ['_endTime'])
| where isempty(['_CoreVersion']) or ExtensionVersion in (_CoreVersion)
| extend ExtensionMode = toint(Properties['common.extensionmode'])
| where ExtensionMode == 1 or ExtensionMode == 2

RawEventsVSCodeExt
| where ExtensionName == "fabric.vscode-fabric"
| where ServerTimestamp between (['_startTime'] .. ['_endTime'])
| distinct ExtensionVersion
| order by parse_version(ExtensionVersion) desc

_events
| where EventName has "item/"
| extend ItemType = tostring(Properties["itemtype"])
| where isnotempty(ItemType)
| distinct ItemType
| order by ItemType asc
